{"tid":2265865,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「香港保衞戰」推續集 皇軍統治港人逃離 居港美籍導演：終有一日，香港會再重光","createTime":"2020-10-31T19:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T04:05:22.000Z","uid":240362,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea7be55fa307f7e33451fe2d79a38cc3404b152","tid":2265865,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T19:52:46.000Z","msg":"預告片: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/Kf0GxCv4TeE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKf0GxCv4TeE&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak4093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=871d19bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Kf0GxCv4TeE</a><br />\n<br />\n若每齣電影總有幾句難忘對白，像《觸目驚心》的「金錢能買走不快樂」，《北非諜影》的「最少我們擁有巴黎」，新戲《香港1942》想必就是：「你要麼移民，要麼與香港同歸於盡」，以及「終有一日，香港會再重光」。<br />\n<br />\n以香港為基地，美籍獨立電影導演Craig McCourry再推新戲，亦是2018年他執導「香港保衞戰」題材電影《1941的聖誕》的續集──電影《柳暗花明淪陷時：香港1942》。預告片已在YouTube發佈，故事講述二戰時一對兄妹在皇軍入侵時，走難到香港，隨即遇上香港淪陷，於是皇軍在香港的鐵腕管治就一幕幕上演──港人被擄入戰俘營、遍體鱗傷的華兵（皇家香港軍團（義勇軍））得不到治療，醫生救人反被追究──似曾相識的情景，經歷去年抗暴之戰的港人應不會陌生，但令人更有切身感受的幾句對白，或使港人更有共鳴，「我要逃離香港，這個淪陷的城市沒有前途」（I need to escape from Hong Kong, there is no future in an occupied city like this）、「你要麼移民，要麼與香港同歸於盡」（You would either immigrate, or you die with it）、「終有一日，香港會再重光」（But someday, Hong Kong will be free again）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/ER4K3ESXYZCSZBZG3UA4QTEX3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FER4K3ESXYZCSZBZG3UA4QTEX3Y%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak4093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=a4222bff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FER4K3ESXYZCSZBZG3UA4QTEX3Y%2F&h=348d5cda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/ER4K3ESXYZCSZBZG3UA4QTEX3Y/</a>"},{"pid":"4af50702ece0cdca6e95d05229ce5a540d803a24","tid":2265865,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T19:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=